title: 550 signatures in 3 days
description: Purely posting on twitter, the petition has received 550 signatures. Thanks you every one who has reposted!

title: From 1 to 120 in 24 hours
description: I am so impressed that a 100 + signatures in one day simply by posting and retweeting on twitter. Thank you to all of you that have signed and reposted. I hope to have 500 signatures in the next 4 days. Please keep up the good work by retweeting and reposting in the days to come.
